text: Kwak Mi-ran (born ) is a South Korean female volleyball player. She was part of the South Korea women's national volleyball team at the 2007 FIVB Volleyball Women's World Cup. ==Clubs== * Korea Highway Corp (2007) ==References== ==External links== *profile at fivb.org * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean women's volleyball players
